#

Caribbean Jerk Chicken Burger

35 min
$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

gluten

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freedairy-free

Cuisine:

Caribbean

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

easyquickspicytropical

Description

A flavorful and spicy chicken burger infused with Caribbean jerk seasoning, topped with tropical slaw and served on a soft bun.

Ingredients

  • ground chicken: 1 lb
  • burger buns: 4
  • cabbage: 2 cups
  • carrot: 1 large
  • mayo: 1/4 cup
  • lime juice: 2 tbsp
  • pineapple slices: 4
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • jerk seasoning: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
